첨부 한 사본 은 의무 기록 원본 과 같음 을 증명 합니다 .
1. Preparation - 환자 에 General anesthesia 시행 후 prone position 으로 눕히고 , Rt , upper back 의 soft tissue mass 노출 시킨 후 , betadine 이용 하여 aseptic preparation and drape 하였다 .

2. Excisional biopsy - Rt . upper back 에서 약 17 x 14 x 4 cm 의 protruding soft movable soft tissue mass 를 확인한 후 , marking pen 으로 oblique incision line 을 design 하였다 . # 15 blade 로 incision line 을 따라 incision 가하여 lipoma 를 노출 시키고 mass 주변부 를 squeezing 하여 abnormal lipoma tissue 를 모두 opening 밖으로 exposure 시켰다 . Lipoma 의 origin identification , normal subcutaneous fat tissue preserve of complete extirpation Ct . Skin flap traction 하여 tension - free wound closure 가능함 을 확인 하고 , antibiotics - mixed N / S 로 irrigation 시행 하였다 . Bovie 로 meticulous bleeding control 한 후 , Flap 을 대략적 으로 approximation 하고 , 3-0 Vicryl 이용 하여 subcutaneous layer 를 simple interrupted suture 하였다 . 1 개의 J / P drain insertion 하고 3-0 Nylon 으로 skin 을 simple interrupted suture 하여 wound closure 하였다 .
3. Dressing - Tarivid ointment , Bactigras , gauze 이용 하여 compressive dressing 시행 하고 수술 을 종료 하였다 .

Under the general anesthesia the pt was placed in lithotomy position , prepped and draped as usual manner .

1. Passed ureteroscope and inserted Terumo guide - wire into the right orifice and after confirming that the guide was placed in renal pelvis by C - arm fluoroscopy , retrieved scope .
2. Advanced double - lumen cahteter with the aid of Terumo guide - wire and inserted Road runner GW .
3. After removal of double - lumen cahteter , advanced access sheath with the aid of guide - wire and removed GW .
4. Advanced flexible ureteroscope until the stone was seen and it was fragmented using Holmium laser and removed using stone basket .
5. Inserted guide - wire via access sheath .

6. RGP was done .
7. DoubleJstent inseted via GW .
8. Foley catheter inserted
